name: KINGSLAYER
description: This is an artifact of a "Kingslayer Clan - Troopers" one of the first alien race who rule the earth 2.0. This Fosil was found in 2122 at Thum-001 Crater. Scientist was fascinated at how advance the technology they had back in the day in fact , they are using all data from their research for "Metaearth Space Program - Space suit". This fossil is not only a priceless artifact but also a sign of hope, the begining of a greater dreams of alien existence on earth. This is the fuel that fire up the spirit of exploration for Metaearth Citizen.
